{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-arrays-and-loops/learn-arrays-and-loops-lesson-e","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"top-learn-arrays-and-loops","challengeType":15,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada, nakon što smo dobili osnovno razumevanje o nizovima podataka, hajde da pričamo o petljama. Petlje se koriste za izvršavanje dela koda više puta. Jedna od tih petlji je petlja <code>while</code>. Petlja <code>while</code> izvršava deo koda samo ako je uslov tačan. Sintaksa petlje za <code>while</code> je sledeća:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">while (condition) {\n  // code block to be executed\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Na primer, deo koda ispod ispisuje brojeve od 1 do 5:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">let i = 1;\nwhile (i &#x3C;= 5) {\n  console.log(i);\n  i++;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Kodni segment iznad inicijalizuje parametar <code>i</code> sa vrednošću <code>1</code>. Petlja <code>while</code> izvršava kodni segment uslovom da je vrednost <code>i</code> manja ili jednaka <code>5</code>. Vrednost <code>i</code> se povećava za <code>1</code> za svaku iteraciju.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Odin","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-arrays-and-loops/learn-arrays-and-loops-lesson-e"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta će biti rezultat ovog fragmenta koda JavaScript ispod?</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">let i = 5;\nwhile (i >= 0) {\n  console.log(i);\n  i--;\n}\n</code></pre>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><code>5</code>, <code>4</code>, <code>3</code>, <code>2</code>, <code>1</code>, <code>0</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>5</code>, <code>4</code>, <code>3</code>, <code>2</code>, <code>1</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>5</code>, <code>4</code>, <code>3</code>, <code>2</code>, <code>1</code>, <code>0</code>, <code>-1</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>1</code>, <code>2</code>, <code>3</code>, <code>4</code>, <code>5</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":1}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","tests":[],"title":"Naučimo o slojevima podataka i ciklusima treninga E","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/the-odin-project/#top-learn-arrays-and-loops","dashedName":"learn-arrays-and-loops-lesson-e","certification":"the-odin-project","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"top-learn-arrays-and-loops","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-arrays-and-loops/learn-arrays-and-loops-lesson-f","prevChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-arrays-and-loops/learn-arrays-and-loops-lesson-d","id":"661e27588602567c118451d5","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":15,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-arrays-and-loops/learn-arrays-and-loops-lesson-e"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}